Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and majestic visual representation of the aseity of God. The image should depict a radiant, timeless being emanating divine light and power, surrounded by symbols of eternity and omnipotence. Include elements such as a glowing halo, celestial clouds, and a sense of infinite presence. The depiction should convey a profound sense of reverence and awe, capturing the essence of God's self-existence and self-sufficiency as described in Christian theology.
